  "text": "In conclusion we can confirm that the terms that are significant in our analysis provide a reasonable biological characterization of the gene groups suggest by Whitfield et al. [CITATION_1] . We can clearly separate mitosis and replication. In addition, our analysis indicates the close relationship of G2-and M-phase, and G1-and S-phase respectively. This example shows that our method can provide useful functional characterization of a given gene group without using prior knowledge. For further examples refer to the supplement [20].",
